question: 응급실에서 바로 ICU로 입실한 환자와 일반 병동을 거쳐 ICU로 입실한 환자의 병원 LOS를 비교해줘.
sql: SELECT icu_admit.icu_type, AVG(admit.los) AS average_los FROM (SELECT icu.SUBJECT_ID, icu.HADM_ID, CASE WHEN trf1.FIRST_CAREUNIT LIKE '%Emergency%' AND trf2.FIRST_CAREUNIT LIKE '%ICU%' THEN 'Direct_ER_to_ICU' WHEN trf1.FIRST_CAREUNIT NOT LIKE '%ICU%' AND trf2.FIRST_CAREUNIT LIKE '%ICU%' THEN 'Ward_to_ICU' ELSE 'Other' END AS icu_type FROM TRANSFERS trf1 INNER JOIN TRANSFERS trf2 ON trf1.SUBJECT_ID = trf2.SUBJECT_ID AND trf1.HADM_ID = trf2.HADM_ID INNER JOIN ICUSTAYS icu ON trf2.SUBJECT_ID = icu.SUBJECT_ID AND trf2.HADM_ID = icu.HADM_ID AND trf2.INTIME = icu.INTIME WHERE icu.FIRST_CAREUNIT IS NOT NULL AND (trf1.FIRST_CAREUNIT LIKE '%Ward%' OR trf1.FIRST_CAREUNIT LIKE '%Emergency%') AND trf2.FIRST_CAREUNIT LIKE '%ICU%') icu_admit JOIN (SELECT SUBJECT_ID, HADM_ID, (CAST(DISCHTIME AS DATE) - CAST(ADMITTIME AS DATE)) AS los FROM ADMISSIONS WHERE ADMITTIME IS NOT NULL AND DISCHTIME IS NOT NULL) admit ON icu_admit.SUBJECT_ID = admit.SUBJECT_ID AND icu_admit.HADM_ID = admit.HADM_ID GROUP BY icu_admit.icu_type

question: 응급실에서 바로 ICU로 입실한 환자와 일반 병동을 거쳐 ICU로 입실한 환자의 병원 LOS를 비교해줘.
sql: SELECT CASE WHEN a.ADMISSION_LOCATION = 'EMERGENCY ROOM' THEN 'Direct to ICU' ELSE 'Via General Ward' END AS admission_path, AVG(s.icustay_los) AS avg_icu_los FROM (SELECT i.SUBJECT_ID, i.HADM_ID, i.STAY_ID, i.intime, i.outtime, LOS AS icustay_los FROM icustays i INNER JOIN admissions a ON i.HADM_ID = a.HADM_ID WHERE a.admit_provider_id IS NOT NULL) s INNER JOIN admissions a ON s.HADM_ID = a.HADM_ID INNER JOIN (SELECT DISTINCT SUBJECT_ID, HADM_ID FROM transfers WHERE eventtype = 'admit' AND FIRST_CAREUNIT = 'ICU') t ON s.SUBJECT_ID = t.SUBJECT_ID AND s.HADM_ID = t.HADM_ID WHERE a.ADMISSION_LOCATION IN ('EMERGENCY ROOM', 'GENERAL WARD') GROUP BY CASE WHEN a.ADMISSION_LOCATION = 'EMERGENCY ROOM' THEN 'Direct to ICU' ELSE 'Via General Ward' END

question: 응급실에서 바로 ICU로 입실한 환자와 일반 병동을 거쳐 ICU로 입실한 환자의 병원 LOS를 비교해줘.
sql:
SELECT ADMISSIONS.SUBJECT_ID, 
       AVG((CAST(ADMISSIONS.DISCHTIME AS DATE) - CAST(ADMISSIONS.ADMITTIME AS DATE))) AS AVG_LOS, 
       TRANSFERS.CAREUNIT AS TRANSFER_PATH
FROM ADMISSIONS
INNER JOIN TRANSFERS ON ADMISSIONS.SUBJECT_ID = TRANSFERS.SUBJECT_ID 
                     AND ADMISSIONS.HADM_ID = TRANSFERS.HADM_ID
WHERE (TRANSFERS.CAREUNIT = 'ICU' AND TRANSFERS.EVENTTYPE = 'TRANSFERS')
GROUP BY ADMISSIONS.SUBJECT_ID, TRANSFERS.CAREUNIT
HAVING COUNT(DISTINCT TRANSFERS.CAREUNIT) = 1 OR
       (COUNT(DISTINCT TRANSFERS.CAREUNIT) > 1 AND MIN(TRANSFERS.CAREUNIT) = 'ICU')

question: 응급실에서 바로 ICU로 입실한 환자와 일반 병동을 거쳐 ICU로 입실한 환자의 병원 LOS를 비교해줘.
응급실에서 바로 ICU로 입실한 환자와 일반 병동을 거쳐 ICU로 입실한 환자의 병원 LOS를 비교해줘.
sql: WITH first_icu AS ( SELECT i.SUBJECT_ID, i.HADM_ID, MIN(i.INTIME) AS FIRST_ICU_INTIME FROM ICUSTAYS i WHERE i.INTIME IS NOT NULL GROUP BY i.SUBJECT_ID, i.HADM_ID ), pre_icu AS ( SELECT f.SUBJECT_ID, f.HADM_ID, MAX(CASE WHEN t.CAREUNIT IS NOT NULL AND UPPER(t.CAREUNIT) NOT LIKE '%ICU%' THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AS HAS_NON_ICU_BEFORE FROM first_icu f LEFT JOIN TRANSFERS t ON t.SUBJECT_ID = f.SUBJECT_ID AND t.HADM_ID = f.HADM_ID AND NVL(t.OUTTIME, t.INTIME) < f.FIRST_ICU_INTIME GROUP BY f.SUBJECT_ID, f.HADM_ID ), path_labeled AS ( SELECT f.SUBJECT_ID, f.HADM_ID, CASE WHEN UPPER(NVL(a.ADMISSION_LOCATION, '')) LIKE '%EMERGENCY%' AND NVL(p.HAS_NON_ICU_BEFORE, 0) = 0 THEN 'Direct_ER_to_ICU' WHEN NVL(p.HAS_NON_ICU_BEFORE, 0) = 1 THEN 'Ward_to_ICU' ELSE 'Other' END AS ICU_PATH FROM first_icu f JOIN ADMISSIONS a ON a.SUBJECT_ID = f.SUBJECT_ID AND a.HADM_ID = f.HADM_ID LEFT JOIN pre_icu p ON p.SUBJECT_ID = f.SUBJECT_ID AND p.HADM_ID = f.HADM_ID ) SELECT l.ICU_PATH, COUNT(*) AS ADMISSION_CNT, AVG(CAST(a.DISCHTIME AS DATE) - CAST(a.ADMITTIME AS DATE)) AS AVG_HOSPITAL_LOS FROM path_labeled l JOIN ADMISSIONS a ON a.SUBJECT_ID = l.SUBJECT_ID AND a.HADM_ID = l.HADM_ID WHERE l.ICU_PATH IN ('Direct_ER_to_ICU', 'Ward_to_ICU') AND a.ADMITTIME IS NOT NULL AND a.DISCHTIME IS NOT NULL GROUP BY l.ICU_PATH ORDER BY l.ICU_PATH

question: 가장 흔한 진단은 무엇인가요?
sql: SELECT b.LONG_TITLE, COUNT(*) as DIAGNOSIS_COUNT FROM DIAGNOSES_ICD a JOIN D_ICD_DIAGNOSES b ON a.ICD_CODE = b.ICD_CODE AND a.ICD_VERSION = b.ICD_VERSION WHERE a.ICD_CODE IS NOT NULL GROUP BY b.LONG_TITLE ORDER BY DIAGNOSIS_COUNT DESC

question: 모든 연령
sql:
SELECT diag_age_group, icd.LONG_TITLE, COUNT(*) AS CNT
FROM (
    SELECT CASE 
               WHEN p.ANCHOR_AGE BETWEEN 0 AND 19 THEN '0-19'
               WHEN p.ANCHOR_AGE BETWEEN 20 AND 39 THEN '20-39'
               WHEN p.ANCHOR_AGE BETWEEN 40 AND 59 THEN '40-59'
               WHEN p.ANCHOR_AGE BETWEEN 60 AND 79 THEN '60-79'
               ELSE '80+' 
           END AS diag_age_group,
           d_icd.ICD_CODE, d_icd.ICD_VERSION
    FROM DIAGNOSES_ICD d_icd
    INNER JOIN PATIENTS p ON d_icd.SUBJECT_ID = p.SUBJECT_ID
    WHERE p.GENDER = 'M'
) age_diag
INNER JOIN D_ICD_DIAGNOSES icd ON age_diag.ICD_CODE = icd.ICD_CODE AND age_diag.ICD_VERSION = icd.ICD_VERSION
WHERE LOWER(icd.LONG_TITLE) LIKE '%heart disease%'
GROUP BY diag_age_group, icd.LONG_TITLE

sql: SELECT p.gender, COUNT(DISTINCT a.HADM_ID) AS CNT FROM ADMISSIONS a INNER JOIN PATIENTS p ON a.SUBJECT_ID = p.SUBJECT_ID WHERE p.gender IS NOT NULL AND a.admittime >= SYSDATE - INTERVAL '30' DAY AND a.admittime < SYSDATE GROUP BY p.gender ORDER BY CNT DESC

question: 성별별 입원 건수 보여줘. (기간: 최근 30일 / 대상 환자: 입원 환자 / 지표: 평균)
sql: SELECT p.gender, COUNT(DISTINCT a.HADM_ID) AS CNT FROM ADMISSIONS a INNER JOIN PATIENTS p ON a.SUBJECT_ID = p.SUBJECT_ID WHERE p.gender IS NOT NULL AND a.admittime >= SYSDATE - INTERVAL '30' DAY AND a.admittime < SYSDATE GROUP BY p.gender ORDER BY CNT DESC

question: COPD 진단 환자의 병원 사망률을 연도별로 보여줘.
전체
sql: SELECT AVG(CAST(ADMISSIONS.DISCHTIME AS DATE) - CAST(ADMISSIONS.ADMITTIME AS DATE)) AS AVG_LOS, AVG(ADMISSIONS.HOSPITAL_EXPIRE_FLAG) AS MORTALITY_RATE FROM ADMISSIONS WHERE ADMISSIONS.ADMITTIME IS NOT NULL AND ADMISSIONS.DISCHTIME IS NOT NULL

question: 평균 입원기간 (기간: 전체 / 대상 환자: 전체 환자 / 지표: 사망률)
sql: SELECT AVG(CAST(ADMISSIONS.DISCHTIME AS DATE) - CAST(ADMISSIONS.ADMITTIME AS DATE)) AS AVG_LOS, AVG(ADMISSIONS.HOSPITAL_EXPIRE_FLAG) AS MORTALITY_RATE FROM ADMISSIONS WHERE ADMISSIONS.ADMITTIME IS NOT NULL AND ADMISSIONS.DISCHTIME IS NOT NULL

question: COPD 진단 환자의 병원 사망률을 연도별로 보여줘
sql: SELECT EXTRACT(YEAR FROM a.ADMITTIME) AS admit_year, SUM(CASE WHEN a.HOSPITAL_EXPIRE_FLAG = 1 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) / COUNT(a.HADM_ID) AS CNT FROM ADMISSIONS a INNER JOIN DIAGNOSES_ICD d ON a.HADM_ID = d.HADM_ID INNER JOIN D_ICD_DIAGNOSES di ON d.ICD_CODE = di.ICD_CODE AND d.ICD_VERSION = di.ICD_VERSION WHERE di.LONG_TITLE LIKE '%COPD%' GROUP BY EXTRACT(YEAR FROM a.ADMITTIME) ORDER BY admit_year

question: COPD 진단 환자의 병원 사망률을 연도별로 보여줘 (기간: 전체 / 대상 환자: COPD 진단 환자 / 지표: 사망률)
sql: SELECT EXTRACT(YEAR FROM a.ADMITTIME) AS admit_year, SUM(CASE WHEN a.HOSPITAL_EXPIRE_FLAG = 1 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) / COUNT(a.HADM_ID) AS CNT FROM ADMISSIONS a INNER JOIN DIAGNOSES_ICD d ON a.HADM_ID = d.HADM_ID INNER JOIN D_ICD_DIAGNOSES di ON d.ICD_CODE = di.ICD_CODE AND d.ICD_VERSION = di.ICD_VERSION WHERE di.LONG_TITLE LIKE '%COPD%' GROUP BY EXTRACT(YEAR FROM a.ADMITTIME) ORDER BY admit_year

question: COPD 진단 환자의 병원 사망률을 연도별로 보여줘
sql: SELECT EXTRACT(YEAR FROM a.admittime) AS admission_year, COUNT(CASE WHEN a.HOSPITAL_EXPIRE_FLAG = 1 THEN 1 END) / COUNT(*) AS CNT FROM DIAGNOSES_ICD d INNER JOIN ADMISSIONS a ON a.HADM_ID = d.HADM_ID WHERE d.icd_code LIKE 'J44%' GROUP BY EXTRACT(YEAR FROM a.admittime) ORDER BY admission_year

question: 대상 환자는 전체 환자로 해줘.
sql: SELECT p.SUBJECT_ID, p.GENDER, p.ANCHOR_AGE, a.ADMITTIME, a.DISCHTIME FROM PATIENTS p INNER JOIN ADMISSIONS a ON p.SUBJECT_ID = a.SUBJECT_ID WHERE a.ADMITTIME >= SYSDATE - INTERVAL '30' DAY AND a.ADMITTIME < SYSDATE

question: 전체 환자를 대상으로 최근 30일 동안의 데이터를 요청합니다.
sql: SELECT p.SUBJECT_ID, p.GENDER, p.ANCHOR_AGE, a.ADMITTIME, a.DISCHTIME FROM PATIENTS p INNER JOIN ADMISSIONS a ON p.SUBJECT_ID = a.SUBJECT_ID WHERE a.ADMITTIME >= SYSDATE - INTERVAL '30' DAY AND a.ADMITTIME < SYSDATE

question: 뇌졸중(허혈성·출혈성 포함) 진단 환자의 병원 사망률을 연도별로 보여줘. (기간: 전체 / 대상 환자: 진단 환자 / 지표: 사망률)
sql: SELECT TO_CHAR(a.ADMITTIME, 'YYYY') AS admission_year, AVG(a.HOSPITAL_EXPIRE_FLAG) AS mortality_rate FROM ADMISSIONS a INNER JOIN DIAGNOSES_ICD d ON a.HADM_ID = d.HADM_ID WHERE d.ICD_CODE LIKE 'I63%' OR d.ICD_CODE LIKE 'I61%' GROUP BY TO_CHAR(a.ADMITTIME, 'YYYY') ORDER BY admission_year
